# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# fukuii-project — baseline .gitignore  (hardened superset)
#
# Inherited by every fukuii-project repo via `fukuii-template`. It is a SUPERSET:
# it protects the secret/artifact shapes of every stack we use (JVM/Scala, Node/JS,
# Go, Python, Rust, Docker/infra) because ONE template seeds them all.
#
# RULE: repos are PUBLIC by default. Never remove the SECURITY blocks below.
# Add repo-specific ignores under the marked section at the bottom.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# == SECURITY: secrets & credentials (never commit) ==
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.*.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.jks
*.keystore
credentials.json
service-account.json
*.credentials
secrets/
.secrets/
*.secret

# == SECURITY: blockchain / node key material ==
/keystore/
wallet.json
mnemonic.txt
*.nodekey
node.key
etc-node.key
jwt.hex
jwtsecret

# == SECURITY: infra / cloud ==
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
.terraform/
*.kubeconfig
kubeconfig
.pgpass
docker-compose.override.yml

# == OS ==
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# == Editors / IDE ==
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.metals/
.bloop/
.bsp/
metals.sbt
.ensime
.ensime_cache/

# == Logs / temp ==
*.log
*.log.*
logs/
tmp/
*.tmp
tmp-*.json
*.pid

# == JVM / Scala / sbt ==
target/
out/
project/boot/
project/plugins/project/
project/project/
project/metals.sbt
*.class

# == Node / JS / TS ==
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.next/
.nuxt/
.turbo/
coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches

# == Go ==
bin/
*.exe
*.test

# == Python ==
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# == Docs build ==
site/
_site/

# == Nix / direnv ==
result
.direnv/
.nix/

# == Claude Code — agentic tooling ==
# Claude Code keeps its runtime state (credentials, session history, checkpoints,
# caches, per-project state, ~/.claude.json) in your HOME dir (~/.claude/), NOT in
# the repo — so the project only needs to ignore the one local settings file, which
# Claude Code auto-ignores anyway. Committed by design: .claude/settings.json,
# .claude/{agents,skills,hooks,commands}/, .mcp.json, AGENTS.md.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/*.local.json

# Personal working/scratch files: prefer `.git/info/exclude` (a per-checkout,
# non-shared ignore) over adding machine-specific patterns to this shared file.
# Vendored reference repos → git submodules or an out-of-tree bootstrap clone.
# Worktrees → sibling dirs OUTSIDE the repo. Task tracking → GitHub Issues/Projects.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Repo-specific ignores BELOW this line (safe to edit per repo):
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
